Type: Package
Package: echoice2
Title: Choice Models with Economic Foundation
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2022-10-30
Author: Nino Hardt (ninohardt.com)
Maintainer: Nino <me@ninohardt.com>
Description: Implements choice/demand models that are rooted in economic
    theory. This is a re-implementation of echoice (v1), with multicore
    computation and tidy principles in mind.
